MOBLEY
v.
O'DONNELL 2018-1417 Supreme Court of Ohio. December 19, 2018

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. O'CONNOR, C.J., and KENNEDY, FRENCH, FISCHER, DEWINE, and DEGENARO, JJ., concur. O'DONNELL, J., not participating.
